{"tid":2388681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！紐約年輕人號召重新佔領華爾街示威　抗議Robinhood限制交易","createTime":"2021-01-31T10:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T18:29:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":319,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd7c2f8d373bb3e3166cbdb65b7c22b322364bb","tid":2388681,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"這班年輕人的所屬組織紐約青年共和黨俱樂部（New York Young Republicans Club，NYYRC）29日在Twitter發文呼籲民眾「帶上標誌並穿上暖和的衣服，1月31日中午12時加入重新佔領華爾街的行動」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNYYRC主席瓦克斯（Gavin Wax）接受《紐約郵報》訪問時說，「過去幾天的事絕對是卑鄙的，這惹惱了很多人。精英和其他階層已無法與金融巨頭一同賺錢獲利。」他的言論顯然是針對美國券商羅賓俠公司（Robinhood）阻止用戶購買遊戲驛站等公司股份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/581666/gme-紐約年輕人號召重新佔領華爾街示威-抗議robinhood限制交易\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F581666%2Fgme-%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0robinhood%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=374e4b28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/581666/gme-紐約年輕人號召重新佔領華爾街示威-抗議robinhood限制交易</a>"},{"pid":"0db1f875a0dfa44eb603826c7a8150aa18a57125","tid":2388681,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f347bd92444292a02af03f089f6231c9a71e66f","tid":2388681,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"